This directory contains some basic examples to demonstrate HClib APIs. 

You must install HClib before building these examples. Please follow the instructions inside $PWD/../../README.md to install HClib.

For building these examples, run the make command inside each subdirectory containing the examples.

For running these examples, use the below command:

HCLIB_WORKERS=<number of threads> ./executable_name [command line arguments (if any)]
